    "class": "name"
   },
   "html": "\n[ ひろせ・たけお ]"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "prof"
   },
   "html": "\n戦艦「朝日」水雷長、ロシア駐在武官、海軍中佐（死後）、「軍神」"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "table",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "off"
   },
   "html": "<tbody><tr><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td></tr></tbody>"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "off"
   },
   "html": "<span class=\"m_r\">エピソード 1</span>調査中。"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "hidden"
   },
   "html": "<a name=\"s1\"></a>\n<a href=\"#s1\">＝</a><a href=\"#h\">△</a><a href=\"#h\">◎</a><a href=\"#s2\">▽</a><a href=\"#s1\">＝</a>"
  },
  {
   "type": "timeline",
   "rows": [
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　大分県出身。海兵15期卒業。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　ロシア留学後、ロシア駐在武官。帰国後、戦艦「朝日」水雷長。日露戦争を迎える。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　<a href=\"../1904/02heso1.html\">旅順口閉塞作戦①</a>に志願し参加。<a href=\"../1904/03heso2.html\">閉塞作戦②</a>でも福井丸を指揮。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　退船直前、杉野孫七上等兵の不在に気づき、船内を捜索。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　福井丸の沈没直前、杉野を見つけられぬまま、左舷のボートに乗り移るも、直後に被弾、戦死。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　この戦死が<a href=\"../1904/03hiros.html\">海軍省によって美談として伝えられ</a>、陸の橘中佐とともに「軍神」と讃えられる。"
      }
     ]
    }
   ]
  },
